trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser> control navigates to a new document whenever one of the following properties is set or methods is called: - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Url%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Navigate%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoForward%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoHome%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoSearch%2A> Handle the `DocumentCompleted` event to receive notification when the new document finishes loading.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser>kontrollen navigerer til et nytt dokument når en av de følgende egenskapene er angitt eller metoder kalles:- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Url%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Navigate%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoForward%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoHome%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoSearch%2A>håndtere den `DocumentCompleted` -hendelsen for å motta varsel når det nye dokumentet innlastingen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoSearch%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoHome%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoForward%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Navigate%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Url%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser>

trans-unit.source: When the `DocumentCompleted` event occurs, the new document is fully loaded, which means you can access its contents through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A>, or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Når den `DocumentCompleted` inntreffer, nytt dokument fullstendig lastes, noe som betyr at du har tilgang til innholdet i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A>, eller <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A>

trans-unit.source: Handling this event lets you cancel navigation if certain conditions have not been met, for example, when the user has not completely filled out a form.
